        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Public Healthcare (SNS)</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
          <li>• <strong>Access:</strong> After contributing to Seguridad Social (or paying convenio especial)</li>
          <li>• <strong>Cost:</strong> Free at point of service</li>
          <li>• <strong>Quality:</strong> Excellent, especially hospitals</li>
          <li>• <strong>Wait times:</strong> Variable by region and specialty</li>
          <li>• <strong>Language:</strong> Spanish primarily</li>
