          <li>• <strong>Access:</strong> With private insurance</li>
          <li>• <strong>Cost:</strong> €100-400+/month insurance</li>
          <li>• <strong>Quality:</strong> Excellent, modern facilities</li>
          <li>• <strong>Wait times:</strong> Short, often same-week</li>
          <li>• <strong>Language:</strong> English common in expat areas</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
